&lt;h1 id="des">DES&lt;/h1>
&lt;blockquote>
&lt;p>参考：&lt;/p>
&lt;ul>
&lt;li>&lt;a href="https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Data_Encryption_Standard">Wiki，Data_Encryption_Standard&lt;/a>&lt;/li>
&lt;li>&lt;a href="https://www.bilibili.com/video/BV1qW4y1L7tN">B 站，【计算机博物志】DES的生与死&lt;/a>&lt;/li>
&lt;/ul>
&lt;/blockquote>
&lt;p>&lt;strong>Data Encryption Standard(数据加密标准)&lt;/strong> 是典型基于 &lt;strong>&lt;a href="https://desistdaydream.github.io/docs/7.%E4%BF%A1%E6%81%AF%E5%AE%89%E5%85%A8/Cryptography/Cipher/Block%20cipher.md">Block cipher&lt;/a>(块密码/分组密码)&lt;/strong> 的加密规范，由于已被破解，被 &lt;a href="https://desistdaydream.github.io/docs/7.%E4%BF%A1%E6%81%AF%E5%AE%89%E5%85%A8/Cryptography/%E5%AF%B9%E7%A7%B0%E5%AF%86%E9%92%A5%E5%8A%A0%E5%AF%86/AES.md">AES&lt;/a> 取代。&lt;/p>
&lt;h1 id="aes">AES&lt;/h1>
&lt;p>&lt;a href="https://desistdaydream.github.io/docs/7.%E4%BF%A1%E6%81%AF%E5%AE%89%E5%85%A8/Cryptography/%E5%AF%B9%E7%A7%B0%E5%AF%86%E9%92%A5%E5%8A%A0%E5%AF%86/AES.md">AES&lt;/a>&lt;/p>
